# range-sum

`Range.map(square).foldLeft(+)` over `0 until 50`, 60 times. Exercises the
`Range` construction + `map` allocation + `foldLeft` reduction path on a
numeric sequence — the only `Range`-driven workload in the corpus.

```scalascript
def workload(): Long =
  var total = 0L
  var k = 0
  while k < 60 do
    val s = (0 until 50).map(i => i * i).foldLeft(0)((a, b) => a + b)
    total = total + s.toLong
    k = k + 1
  total
```
